ComicInfo.Summary:
Atomic Robo and his followers find themselves getting more than they bargained for at national science fair when Dr. Dinosaur comes to steal Emma Armstrong's science project for his own insidious purposes. In addition this issue offers a glimpse into the world of Foster Broussard and the Demons of the Gold Rush (to be on comic shelves in May) as well as Moon Girl.
